  "texts": [
    "While some parameters, like the target risk, are given, others are less obvious.",
    "For example, how should we choose γ trade?",
    "The default value of one is our best guess of what the single period transaction cost will be.",
    "But perhaps we get better performance with γ trade = 2, which means, roughly speaking, that we are exaggerating trading cost by a factor of two.",
    "The result, of course, is a reduction in trading compared to the default value one."
